HEADWORD: Epigrammatizer
<hw>Ep`i*gram"ma*ti`zer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
writes in an affectedly pointed style.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Epigrammatizers</qex> of our English prose style.</q>
